description: Police warn of incident at Manchester Arena in England during a concert by pop singer and actress Ariana Grande.
title: Police warn of incident at Manchester Arena  - CNN Video

author: By Thomas Burrows, Rory Tingle and Jake Wallis Simons For Mailonline
description: Nineteen people have been confirmed dead and around 50 injured after a terrorist attack inside Manchester Arena at the end of a teen concert tonight.
title: BREAKING NEWS: Emergency services rush to Manchester Arena

author: Tom Batchelor
description: Multiple people have died at Manchester Arena following a reported explosion at an Ariana Grande concert, police have said. Footage shows thousands of panicked young people fleeing the arena  covered in blood and crying, although it is not immediately clear what the reported "loud bangs" were.
title: 19 confirmed dead and 50 injured after reported explosion at Manchester Arena – live updates

description: Witnesses speak of a huge bomb-like bang going off and seeing everyone flee Manchester Arena. Follow live.
title: Live: 'Suddenly there was this massive explosion': Witnesses relay concert chaos

author: BBC News
description: Police say nineteen people have died and about 50 are injured in an explosion at Manchester Arena.
title: Manchester incident: Latest updates

author: Samantha Beech and Darran Simon, CNN
description: At least 19 people are dead and about 50 injured in a possible terrorist incident Monday at Manchester Arena in England, where pop singer Ariana Grande was performing, Greater Manchester Police said.
title: British police: 19 dead after blast at Ariana Grande concert in Manchester

author: CNBC
description: At least 20 people were killed Monday night at an Ariana Grande concert at Manchester Arena in England, multiple law enforcement told NBC News.
title: At least 20 dead after explosion heard at Ariana Grande UK concert

description: A witness at Ariana Grande's concert inside of Manchester Arena in England said there were little girls crying after reports of an explosion inside the venue.
title: Witness at Ariana Grande event describes chaos - CNN Video

author: Harriet Sinclair
description: A number of people were killed in the blast, which took place outside the Manchester Arena. The singer's people have confirmed she is 'okay' following the incident.
title: Police confirm 19 fatalities in explosion at Ariana Grande concert in Manchester

author: Andrew Buncombe
description: Witnesses told of scenes of horror and chaos as they fled from an Ariana Grande concert in Manchester after police responded to reports of an explosion. People said the concert by the US singer had just concluded and the lights in the Manchester Arena had come on when there was a loud blast.
title: Manchester eyewitness speaks out: 'People have said it was a speaker or balloons but it wasn’t. It was explosions'
